	(178,8,'2013-04-24 17:59:25','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Not that we didn\'t know already, but Karin Fong\'s <em>God of War</em> trailer, \"For Ashes,\" is one of the best pieces of VFX/Animation out there.  <a href=\"http://www.shootonline.com/go/news-view.rs-web3-1541598-1366382924-2.Visual-Effects---Animation---i-SHOOT--i--s-2013-Spring-Top-Ten-Chart.html\">SHOOT Online</a> recognized it too and listed the Imaginary Forces director\'s work among their top 10.  And because it\'s impossible not to become obsessed with this spot, here it is again for you to enjoy.\r\n\r\n[jwplayer mediaid=\"1819\"]','God of VFX','','draft','open','open','','','','','2013-04-24 17:59:25','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=178',297,'post','',0),
	(179,8,'2013-07-29 19:02:36','0000-00-00 00:00:00','By now we all know how awesome the opening and ending credit sequences were for Guillermo del Toro\'s \"Pacific Rim,\" thanks to the beautiful artistry from <a href=\"imaginaryforces.com\">Imaginary Forces</a>.  In a new interview with IF creative director, Miguel Lee, we learn a little more about the process and the behind the scenes magic making.  Check it out <a href=\"http://www.artofvfx.com/?p=4793\">here</a>.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2141\" title=\"Untitled\" src=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site_2/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Untitled.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"644\" height=\"363\" />','IF and Guillermo del Toro have even more to say','','draft','open','open','','','','','2013-07-29 19:02:36','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=179',296,'post','',0),
	(180,8,'2014-01-06 20:12:16','0000-00-00 00:00:00','We\'re excited to announce the arrival of our newest Family Member, Dalice Shilshtut!  She\'s our favorite new kid sister and already an awesome asset to the team.  She\'s a lover of all things Bill Cosby and she\'s got the Facebook picture to prove it.  Welcome aboard Dalice!\n\n<img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-2442\" title=\"1391966_10103111143156059_925710547_n\" src=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site_2/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/1391966_10103111143156059_925710547_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"403\" height=\"403\" />','New Year, New Blood','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-01-06 20:12:16','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=180',295,'post','',0),
