	(249,2,'2010-01-04 16:31:30','2010-01-04 16:31:30','HI Family Friends,\r\n\r\nWelcome to a new year and a new decade. We are really freaking excited. Are you? You should be. A new year is a clean slate and a new decade is a blank canvas ready to be painted with all the amazing things we will do and create.\r\n\r\nWe plan on making MAGIC happen here and you will have many things to look forward to from us.  The first of which will be a new look and a new website.\r\n\r\nAlso, we will be ready to officially announce a new Family Member later this week.\r\n\r\nAren\'t we off to an incredible start??  We are.\r\n\r\nAlthough, minor setback. Our phones here in the office are not working. So no one can call us, and we can call no one. Huh. Do you think that\'s a sign? We do. We think it\'s a sign that no matter what, The Family succeeds.\r\n\r\nGo ahead, take our phones - we\'ll just email you. What? Our internet went down? Who cares! We\'ve got mobile phones with internet capabilities, and this office is one of the few places on earth that Chris\' iPhone actually works. So, see? Nothing will keep us down.\r\n\r\nGet ready Ad World, this is the year of US.\r\n\r\n(it\'s also the year of the tiger, grrr)','SUCCESS IN THE FACE OF ADVERSITY (aka F.U. Verizon)','','publish','open','open','','success-in-the-face-of-adversity-aka-f-u-verizon','','','2010-01-04 16:31:30','2010-01-04 16:31:30','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=249',226,'post','',0),
