	(251,2,'2010-01-27 18:34:25','2010-01-27 18:34:25','The Family is always exploring its roots.  Recently, Diane found out that her family - The Patrones - hail from a town in Italy called <a href=\"http://www.italyworldclub.com/campania/avellino/bagnoliirpino.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Bagnoli Irpino</a> in the Avellino province. And Chris recently found out that The Zanders may secretly be related to the <a href=\"http://www.upjohn.org.uk/weupjohn.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Upjohn</a> Family.\r\n\r\nAnd now we have a new relation with a German name: The Family would like to announce its newest member, <a href=\"http://www.ubercontent.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Über Content</a>!\r\n\r\nLook for exciting things to come from this new relationship, including some interesting pizza and beer <a href=\"http://chowhound.chow.com/topics/574190\" target=\"_blank\">pairings</a> at our screenings.','LA FAMIGLIA GOES GERMAN','','publish','open','open','','la-famiglia-goes-german','','','2010-01-27 18:34:25','2010-01-27 18:34:25','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=251',224,'post','',0),
	(252,2,'2010-02-12 18:33:09','2010-02-12 18:33:09','This entry serves two purposes.\r\n\r\n#1 It announces that director <a href=\"http://believemedia.wiredrive.com/library/preview_presentation/?p=7b091d4bf2b6ed4576ec18b8f85cf7a5\">WAYNE HOLLOWAY</a> has joined the roster at Believe Media. Awesome!\r\n\r\n#2 It announces the launch of his new viral campaign for Samsung and their sponsorhip at the 2010 Olympic games. Awesomer!\r\n\r\nSamsung is sponsoring a contest for its mobile phone users<a href=\"http://mobileexplorers.ca.msn.com/\">http://mobileexplorers.ca.msn.com/ </a>to encourage them to find outrageous moments at the olympics and shoot them with their phones. Wayne Holloway was hired to recreate some <a href=\"http://believemedia.wiredrive.com/library/preview_presentation/?p=0bb1ec86f53a87506ef9eeb646cb5644\">outrageous moments</a> . They are being released <a href=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site/news/www.youtube.com\">virally</a> and so far have received more than 2,000,000 hits. Awesomest!','SAMSUNG SNOWBALL SLAMDUNK','','publish','open','open','','samsung-snowball-slamdunk','','','2010-02-12 18:33:09','2010-02-12 18:33:09','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=252',223,'post','',0),
	(253,2,'2010-03-05 18:32:38','2010-03-05 18:32:38','Mentors.  They are amazing forces in our lives. They shape and mold you, show you the ropes, and if you are lucky enough to get a great one - he or she can get you started on the path to a great career. Debbie McMurtrey was lucky enough.  She had <a href=\"http://cuttingroom.wiredrive.com/l/p/?presentation=8b051944ae4ad6a876602d571fded414\" target=\"_blank\">Chuck Willis</a> as a mentor.  Ten years ago, after growing up in Chicago and graduating from college where she fell upon editing by chance, Debbie moved to NYC. Chuck Willis gave Debbie her start as his assistant editor at Crew Cuts.  She worked her way up to become a full editor there.\r\n\r\nTwo years ago, Debbie was asked to start the NY office of Nomad Editorial. Now, she is once again working alongside her mentor.  Debbie is the latest editor to join <a href=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site/news/www.cuttingroom.tv\">Cutting Room</a>.  You can find her in Room 4, right next to Room 3 where you can find Chuck Willis.  Full Circle.  Welcome home Debbie!\r\n\r\nTo learn more about Debbie, click <a href=\"http://presskitchenblog.wordpress.com/2010/03/03/cutting-room-beefs-up-its-roster-with-editor-debbie-mc-murtrey-2/\" target=\"_blank\">here </a>for the press release about her joining Cutting Room.\r\n\r\nTo view some highlights of her work, click <a href=\"http://cuttingroom.wiredrive.com/l/p/?presentation=fa2965ebb9d3d72569486dc7862bf596\" target=\"_blank\">here</a> .','FULL CIRCLE: the abbreviated story of editor Debbie McMurtrey','','publish','open','open','','full-circle-the-abbreviated-story-of-editor-debbie-mcmurtrey','','','2010-03-05 18:32:38','2010-03-05 18:32:38','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=253',222,'post','',0),
	(254,2,'2010-03-10 18:29:49','2010-03-10 18:29:49','CHERRY BOMB! QUEENS OF NOISE! NEON ANGELS ON THE ROAD TO RUIN!\r\n\r\nAll killer/famous tracks from game changing punk bandThe Runaways, that we may now relive on the big screen thanks to director Floria Sigismondi.\r\n\r\nFloria Sigismondi has long been associated with rock &amp; roll. Her acclaimed music video work for the likes of Muse, The Cure, The Whitestripes, and Christina Aguilera is astonishingly beautiful, insanely creative and always cutting edge. Her commercial work is iconic. Her photography is world renowned. And now she\'s combined all her prowess and poured in into independent film, writing and directing the rebellious rock-n-roll biopic of Joan Jett and the greatest girl band ever, The Runaways.  A defining punk rock band that established Joan Jett as a badass, being brought to you by another badass, Floria Sigismondi. It\'s just the perfect match.  No one else could have brought this story to life the way Floria has. AND it stars two of the most formidable teen-aged actresses in Hollywood, Kristen Stewart and Dakota Fanning. How crazy perfect awesome is that?!\r\n\r\nCheck out the trailer <a href=\"http://believemedia.wiredrive.com/l/p/?presentation=d9e4860231f9c68628550eddca448b77\" target=\"_blank\">here</a> .\r\n\r\nCheck out highlights of Floria\'s work <a href=\"http://believemedia.wiredrive.com/l/p/?presentation=1fbf7f3013623595fa974da71b5c6558\" target=\"_blank\">here</a> .\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site_2/?attachment_id=237\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-237\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-237\" title=\"sigismondi-therunaways-full\" src=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site_2/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/sigismondi-therunaways-full-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>','FLORIA SIGISMONDI: The new Queen of Noise','','publish','open','open','','floria-sigismondi-the-new-queen-of-noise','','','2010-03-10 18:29:49',