	(259,2,'2010-03-19 18:25:12','2010-03-19 18:25:12','<span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva;\">WELCOME HOME, ANNA.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva;\">Six years ago, Anna Rotholz held the title of the first \"Little Sis\" in The Family.  Since then, our little sister has gone on to some amazing things with her career; representing Spotwelders, Squeak E Clean, Thomas Thomas, Picture Mill, and Outside Edit to name a few. Lil\' Sis grew up. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva;\">But you know what they say at the Olive Garden, \"once you\'re here, you\'re family.\" That really could not be more true in this case as Anna is now (and has always been) a member of The Family. We could not be happier, nor more proud, to welcome her back as \"Another Sister.\"</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva;\">She can be reached at <a href=\"mailto:anna@thefamilynyc.com\">anna@thefamilynyc.com</a> or 212.477.4278.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva;\">The Family now includes Diane Patrone, Chris Zander, Anna Rotholz, Sean Mihlo, Backyard, Believe Media, Cutting Room, HunterGatherer, Imaginary Forces, and Über Content.</span>','HAPPY JOY EXCITEMENT!','','publish','open','open','','happy-joy-excitement','','','2010-03-19 18:25:12','2010-03-19 18:25:12','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=259',218,'post','',0),
	(260,2,'2010-08-31 18:22:16','2010-08-31 18:22:16','We are excited to announce the addition of director K-roll to the Believe Media roster. Hailing from Paris, she is one of the top new talents working in France and Europe and we are thrilled to introduce her to the US market. Her highly conceptual, fresh and sexy style blossomed after graduating in Beaux Arts and pursuing her interest in graphic design.  K-roll ventured into advertising and worked for many years as a top creative at select agencies in Paris. Her move into directing commercials and music videos was a natural progression that has since allowed her to put her stamp on the industry from the other side of the camera.With an expertise for beauty, fashion and storytelling (a combination that is rarely found in one director) she has directed spots for Nina Ricci, Martin Grant and Virginie Castaway.\r\n\r\nTo see K-roll\'s reel, click <a href=\"http://www.believemedia.com/director.php?director_id=74&amp;reel_id=2855\" target=\"_blank\">here.</a>','K-ROLL JOINS BELIEVE MEDIA','','publish','open','open','','k-roll-joins-believe-media','','','2010-08-31 18:22:16','2010-08-31 18:22:16','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=260',217,'post','',0),
