	(314,2,'2011-10-13 20:10:50','2011-10-13 20:10:50','Cutting Room, Cutting Room, Cutting Room. It\'s all we hear these days, and we like it!  Everyday there is a new mention of them in the press, be it for the suspense/action/dramatic series they cut for the FX Network and Audi (directed by the awesome Daniel Minahan of \"Game of Thrones\"), or the super fun they cut for Dave Meyers and BBDO, or  the latest work for Dish Network out of BFG9000, or their infamous Halloween Party, everyone is talking about Cutting Room.  In case you are one of the few who isn\'t buzzing about CR, here are a few links to check out so you can get in the know and start talking!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/news/advertising-branding/ad-day-dish-network-135482\">Dish Network, Ad of the Day</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://creativity-online.com/work/dish-network-celebration/24686\">Dish Network on Creativity</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.campaignlive.co.uk/thework/login/1095647/\">Lowes in Campaign Magazine</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.shootonline.com/go/index.php?name=Articles&amp;op=view&amp;id=rs-web4-982794-1317906669-2\">Shoot feature on Audi</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/drivers-seat/2011/09/23/audi-casts-a6-sedan-in-jersey-city-film/\">Wall St Journal feature on Audi</a>\r\n\r\nIf this is not enough to strike up a Cutting Room Conversation, visit <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cuttingroomfilms\">their facebook page!</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[wiredrive hidethumbs=\"off\" disablethumbs=\"off\" theme=\"grid\"]http://www.wdcdn.net/rss/presentation/library/client/cuttingroom/id/7c34c462432de06d911c2d49a7222874/[/wiredrive]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Cutting Room, Cutting Room, Cutting Room!','','publish','open','open','','cutting-room-cutting-room-cutting-room','','','2011-10-13 20:10:50','2011-10-13 20:10:50','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=314',167,'post','',0),
