	(327,2,'2012-03-21 16:45:35','2012-03-21 16:45:35','We feel that our favorite quote by Ted \"Theodore\" Logan in one of our favorite movies, Bill &amp; Ted\'s Excellent Adventure, is apropos for announcing new Family Member, Daniel Strange, who joined <a href=\"http://www.ubercontent.com\" target=\"_blank\">Über Content</a> this month.\r\n\r\nMuch like how the oddball comedy of the 1989 cult classic movie was cutting edge for it\'s time....Daniel Strange \'s style of comedy that he\'s created in the hilarious and offbeat Funny or Die series \"Between Two Ferns\"with Zach Galifianakis is sure to be a comedic benchmark for generations to come.  His notable episodes include guests <a href=\"http://www.funnyordie.com/videos/477f3b6bc5/between-two-ferns-with-zach-galifianakis-from-between-two-ferns-comedy-deathray-and-zach-galifianakis\" target=\"_blank\">John Hamm</a>, <a href=\"http://www.funnyordie.com/videos/5ef1adb57b/between-two-ferns-with-zach-galifianakis\" target=\"_blank\">Natalie Portman</a>, <a href=\"http://www.funnyordie.com/videos/6ae880a42b/between-two-ferns-with-zach-galifianakis\" target=\"_blank\">Bradley Cooper</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.funnyordie.com/videos/60072add5a/between-two-ferns-with-zach-galifianakis-ben-stiller\" target=\"_blank\">Ben Stiller</a>.\r\n\r\nWe here at The Family feel that we will have a most triumphant time helping to break Strange into the commercial market, and he\'s off to a great start with a 22 spot web campaign for Toyota out of Saatchi LA. Excellent! Party on, Dude!  (Sorry, we sometimes get carried away when it comes to Bill &amp; Ted.)','Strange things are afoot at the Circle K....','','publish','open','open','','strange-things-are-afoot-at-the-circle-k','','','2012-03-21 16:45:35','2012-03-21 16:45:35','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=327',157,'post','',0),
