	(374,8,'2013-02-19 23:08:05','2013-02-19 23:08:05','America\'s favorite weatherman, Al Roker, teams up with Xander from Backyard to bring us the Ad Council\'s latest spot on storm preparedness.  As we Sandy survivors know all too well, a storm surge can come on like a mother, and we all need to be prepared.  Xander and his team perfectly captured the essence of a sunny day that gives way to armageddon.  With green screen and special effects, he masterfully directs his weather elements as well as his weather man and the result is a memorable and impactful psa.  The Today Show crew goes behind the scenes on this spot and we even get to hear from Xander himself.  Check out this clip and remember...bottled water and batteries!\r\n\r\n[youtube aWWP6gFRYks]','And that\'s the latest weather from your neck of the woods','','publish','open','open','','and-thats-the-latest-weather-from-your-neck-of-the-woods','','','2013-02-19 23:08:05','2013-02-19 23:08:05','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=374',118,'post','',0),
