	(383,8,'2013-04-16 20:49:37','2013-04-16 20:49:37','In his latest spot for Goodyear, <a href=\"http://www.backyard.com/directors/nick--piper\" target=\"_blank\">Nick Piper</a> puts rubber to the road, literally.  From the engineers and factory workers to the race drivers themselves, we follow the course of the iconic tires and the thrill of Nascar is alive throughout.  So even when you\'re driving your Camaro, you can feel the pulse of Nascar when you\'re rolling on America\'s top tire.  Piper teamed up with <a href=\"http://www.backyard.com/about\" target=\"_blank\">Backyard\'s Kris Mathur </a>as executive producer, and the two crafted a checkered flag winning spot.  Check it out below.\r\n\r\n[jwplayer mediaid=\"1920\"]','Battle Tested, Road Ready','','publish','open','open','','battle-tested-road-ready','','','2013-04-16 20:49:37','2013-04-16 20:49:37','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=383',109,'post','',0),
