	(388,8,'2013-04-30 22:28:52','2013-04-30 22:28:52','<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2016\" title=\"union logo\" src=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site_2/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/union-logo-300x205.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"205\" />\r\n\r\nFamily is all about being united, having reunions, being a unit. Well,  we are now<em> </em>a united Family unit with <a href=\"http://www.unioneditorial.com/\">Union Editorial</a> and we could not be happier with this new bundle of post production joy.  Union houses some of the best bi-coastal editors in the biz.  If you\'ve seen it, Union\'s probably cut it.  Their portfolio includes award-winning commercial spots, memorable Superbowl ads, huge blockbuster trailers, unforgettable music videos, and more.  Our <em>union</em> with Union is so kismet, they even have a sister too!  Sister company, Resolution, is also best in their class with VFX.  We are thrilled to join forces with Union and Resolution and we\'re positively <em>resolute</em> about representing all our new family members!','Family (Re)Union','','publish','open','open','','family-reunion','','','2013-04-30 22:28:52','2013-04-30 22:28:52','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=388',105,'post','',0),
