	(412,8,'2013-10-01 14:54:30','2013-10-01 14:54:30','No one does creepy weird quite like <a href=\"http://www.believemedia.com/floria-sigismondi/\">Floria Sigismondi</a>.  In the <a href=\"http://www.believemedia.com/\">Believe</a> director\'s latest effort, a music video for Lawrence Rothman\'s \"#1 All Time Low,\" she takes the genre to new extremes.  But her artistry is so compelling and captivating that not even a dystopian setting and bloody bathwater can turn you away.  <a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/09/16/lawrence-rothman-1-all-time-low-video_n_3934495.html\">Huffington Post</a> refers to it as \"the creepiest thing you\'ll see today\" and we like to think of that as a compliment.  Thanks HuffPo, and kudos to Floria!\r\n\r\n[youtube 4LCev_bkR6o nolink]','Floria Gets Creepy','','publish','open','open','','floria-gets-creepy','','','2013-10-01 14:54:30','2013-10-01 14:54:30','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=412',82,'post','',0),
