	(455,2,'2014-04-21 18:48:58','2014-04-21 18:48:58','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">What\'s beautiful about Believe Media?  The amazing talent, the team, and their happy clients. They\'ve been the stand out in the Fashion &amp; Beauty market for years with directors Bruno Aveillan, Floria Sigismondi, Jake Nava, and Tryan George setting the standard. Bruno\'s most famous for his work on Cartier but his effort on Shalimar for Guerlain was epic; Floria\'s new spot for Thierry Mugler is stunning. Tryan\'s been setting the looks for Pantene all over the globe.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-2604\" title=\"Thierry Mugler Alien by Floria Sigismondi\" src=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site_2/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Alien_700x330.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"441\" height=\"208\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">More recent stars are Parisienne Carole Denis and Mary Rozzi who have both been doing gorgeous lifestyle work for Olay; Sara Marandi who just wrapped Tina Fey\'s new campaign for Garnier, and the Swedish sensation Daniel Skoglund who just wrapped up a big campaign for Maybelline and Louis Vuitton.  The Source has gotten to the essence of Believe\'s beautiful success in this weeks\' focus story. <a title=\"Click here for more! \" href=\"http://sourceecreative.com/news-or-feature-story.php?type=sf&amp;ID=78&amp;a=1\" target=\"_blank\">Click here for more!</a></p>','The Beauty of Believe','','publish','open','open','','the-beauty-of-believe','','','2014-04-21 18:48:58','2014-04-21 18:48:58','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=455',45,'post','',0),
	(456,1,'2014-05-06 19:49:54','2014-05-06 19:49:54','[youtube da5tjfpKyac nolink]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWho needs checks and balances when you could just check out this hilarious new work from <a href=\"http://www.believemedia.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Believe Media\'s</a> Maurice Marable for the White House Correspondents\' Dinner, starring VEEP star Julia Louis Dreyfus and the actual current Vice President of the United States, Joe Biden.\r\n\r\nOur favorite real life, and our favorite  fictional VEEP  work their way through DC\'s most exclusive address on Pennsylvania Avenue, while running into some special guests along the way.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis tongue-in-cheeck depiction of a day in Washington not only <a href=\"http://www.vanityfair.com/online/daily/2014/04/veep-joe-video-biden-white-house-correspondents-dinner\" target=\"_blank\">WOWS</a>, but is also <a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/video-joe-biden-julia-louis-dreyfus-intro-to-whcd-2014-5#!JHLQv\" target=\"_blank\">EPIC</a> according to the press... however the press is definitely bias on this one.... being that it was shown at the pening of their famed appreciation dinner.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nRegardless, this short film is the kind of bipartisanship we can all laugh at.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2707\" src=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site_2/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Untitled.tiff\" alt=\"WHCD\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2710\" src=\"http://www.thefamilynyc.com/previous_site_2/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/WHCD-263x300.jpg\" alt=\"WHCD\" width=\"263\" height=\"300\" />','US Politics... Funny Business.','','publish','open','open','','us-politics-funny-business','','','2014-05-06 19:49:54','2014-05-06 19:49:54','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=456',44,'post','',0),
	(457,1,'2014-06-18 18:40:52','2014-06-18 18:40:52','Have you been suffering from overly serious slacks? Well, these commercials are for you.  <a href=\"http://backyard.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Backyard\'s</a>   <a href=\"http://backyard.com/directors/seth--townsend\" target=\"_blank\">Seth Townsend</a>, Dockers and the creatives at Red Tettemer O\'Connell + Partners teamed up to create these hilarious yet melodramatic PSA spoofs,  highlighting the pain and suffering Dad Pants inflict unknowingly on their loved ones.  Sarah Harbaugh, wife of San Francisco 49ers coach Jim Harbaugh, talks about their journey to better fitting britches.\r\n\r\n[youtube yeW81D5uqcw nolink]\r\n\r\nIf you, or someone you know, suffer from Dad Pant, there is hope. Look no further than former Tampa Bay Buccaneers head coach Jon Gruden.  He gives a healthy dose of encouragement to all the dads out there.\r\n\r\n[youtube zrWzhiAN5Uk nolink]\r\n<div>The consumer and the industry have truly embraced these spots... leading us to beleive that  <a href=\"http://www.fastcocreate.com/3031834/dockers-warns-men-against-the-evils-of-dad-pants\" target=\"_blank\">Fast Company</a>, <a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/adfreak/sarah-harbaugh-and-jon-gruden-fight-scourge-dad-pants-dockers-158344\" target=\"_blank\">Ad Week</a>, <a href=\"http://www.complex.com/style/2014/06/jim-harbaugh-cures-dad-pants-with-dockers\" target=\"_blank\">Complex</a>, <a href=\"http://www.mediabistro.com/agencyspy/rtop-sarah-harbaugh-seek-to-stop-dad-pants-for-dockers_b67047\" target=\"_blank\">Agency Spy</a>,  <a href=\"http://mashable.com/2014/06/12/jim-harbaugh-dockers-dads-pants/\" target=\"_blank\">Mashable</a>,  <a href=\"http://www.bestadsontv.com/news/blog.php?id=25785\" target=\"_blank\">Best Ads on TV</a>,  <a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/john-mccormick/in-defense-of-dad-pants_b_5496813.html\" target=\"_blank\">Huff Post</a>, and  <a href=\"http://devour.com/video/stop-dad-pants/\" target=\"_blank\">Devour</a>  there are more than a few fathers in need of new pants. t</div>','Dad Pants are no Laughing Matter','','publish','open','open','','dad-pants-are-no-laughing-matter','','','2014-06-18 18:40:52','2014-06-18 18:40:52','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=457',43,'post','',0),
