	(467,1,'2014-06-23 19:10:37','2014-06-23 19:10:37','We are so proud to announce that <a href=\"http://www.believemedia.com/derin-seale/\" target=\"_blank\">Derin Seale</a> of <a href=\"http://www.believemedia.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Believe Media</a>, in his partnership with Clemenger BBDO, has won THREE Lions at Cannes!  Derin\'s powerful, emotionally stirring and visually captivating work for the New Zealand Transport Agency brings home the message of how precious life is and what a difference a moment can make.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[youtube bvLaTupw-hk]</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe\'re not the only ones that took notice of how incredible this work is. After winning the <a href=\"https://www.shootonline.com/spw/derin-seale-wins-one-show-gold-pencil-advertising-nzta-psa-mistakes\" target=\"_blank\">Golden Pencil</a> at this year\'s ONE Show it comes as no surprise that the spot took home the Bronze for Script, Silver for Director and Gold for Film!  Here is a wonderful interview <a href=\"http://sourceecreative.com/news-or-feature-story.php?type=news&amp;ID=8443\" target=\"_blank\">SourceECreative</a> has done with Derin on his process in helping curate such an effective campaign. Congratulations to Derin and the whole Believe team!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Cannes You BELIEVE It!','','publish','open','open','','cannes-you-believe-it','','','2014-06-23 19:10:37','2014-06-23 19:10:37','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=467',33,'post','',0),
