	(496,2,'2014-10-09 17:33:58','2014-10-09 17:33:58','Rock The Vote...asks what are you going to turn out for this election? Global Warming Reform? Gun Control? Marriage Equality? Whatever the reason, Lil John and his famous friends want to make sure you\'re registered to rock the vote. <a href=\"http://www.whitehousepost.com/editors/new-york/trish-fuller/reel/\" target=\"_blank\">Trish Fuller</a> of <a href=\"http://www.whitehousepost.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Whitehouse Post</a> has joined the bandwagon, and it\'s time to spread the word--Midterm Elections are November 4th. This spot\'s gone viral and it\'s time to catch up on the hype at <a href=\"http://www.buzzfeed.com/reggieugwu/rock-the-vote#3r0jbce\" target=\"_blank\">BuzzFeed,</a> <a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/laura-reyes/turnoutforwhat-our-values_b_5939010.html\" target=\"_blank\">Huffington Post,</a> <a href=\"http://nypost.com/2014/10/07/lil-jon-lena-dunham-rock-the-vote-in-turn-out-for-what/\" target=\"_blank\">NYPost,</a> <a href=\"Rock%20the Vote....asks what are you going to turn out for this election?  Global Warming Reform? Gun Control? Marriage Equality?  Whatever the reason, Lil John and his famous friends want to make sure you are registered to rock the vote. Trish Fuller of Whitehouse Post has join the bandwagon, and it’s time to spread the word—Elections are November 4th. This spot’s gone viral and it’s time to catch up on the buzz on Rollhttp://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/lena-dunham-lil-jon-team-for-rock-the-votes-turn-out-for-what-video-20141007\" target=\"_blank\">Rolling Stone</a> and <a href=\"http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/web-to-watch/2014/10/07/web-to-watch-lil-jon-turn-out-for-what-rock-the-vote/16889173/\" target=\"_blank\">USA Today</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[youtube rijpU5yD55I nolink]</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','#TURNOUTFORWHAT','','publish','open','open','','turnoutforwhat','','','2014-10-09 17:33:58','2014-10-09 17:33:58','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=496',4,'post','',0),
	(497,1,'2015-04-10 19:49:20','2015-04-10 19:49:20','You might want to think twice before getting behind the wheel. <a href=\"http://capguncollective.com/directors/Tomas-Mankovsky\" target=\"_blank\">Tomas Mankovsky</a> of <a href=\"http://capguncollective.com\" target=\"_blank\">Cap Gun Collective </a> commands your attention in this emotionally stirring spot for the Transport Accident Commission. This wasn\'t an easy task as the \"spot was filmed in a single take, requiring a perfectly timed and synchronized performance from both of them [father and son]...\" but Tomas\' hard work paid off as \"Strings\" was featured as AdWeek\'s <a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/news/advertising-branding/ad-day-artfully-chilling-psa-shows-how-kids-learn-your-bad-driving-habits-163988\" target=\"_blank\">AD OF THE DAY!</a> Be sure to catch up on the rest of the shout outs on <a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/agencyspy/clemenger-bbdo-pulls-strings-for-transport-accident-commission/84089\" target=\"_blank\">AgencySpy</a>,  <a href=\"http://adland.tv/commercials/tac-strings-what-kind-driver-are-you-raising-2015-60-australia\" target=\"_blank\">Adland</a> and <a href=\"http://www.thedrum.com/news/2015/04/10/ad-day-transport-accident-commission-strings\" target=\"_blank\">The Drum. </a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[youtube opoGqpDfPAY nolink]</p>','Test Drive','','publish','open','open','','test-drive','','','2015-04-10 19:49:20','2015-04-10 19:49:20','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=497',3,'post','',0),
	(498,1,'2015-04-13 14:25:39','2015-04-13 14:25:39','Nothing\'s worse than waking up to an influx of emails flooding your mailbox, pinging with an incessant notification that your inbox is full. Well, <a href=\"http://bullypictures.com/directors/?director=8\" target=\"_blank\">Tripp &amp; Tyler</a> of <a href=\"http://bullypictures.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Bully Pictures</a> are at it again with another honest and completely relatable office stunt after their hilarious video, <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DYu_bGbZiiQ\" target=\"_blank\">\"A Conference Call in Real Life,\"</a> turned viral. That\'s right, \"Email in Real Life\" sets out to capture annoyingly bad email habits and our everyday robot like responses. Maybe it\'s time we switch up the endless auto responses and text heavy signature lines.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[youtube HTgYHHKs0Zw nolink]</p>','Email Etiquette 101','','publish','open','open','','email-etiquette-101','','','2015-04-13 14:25:39','2015-04-13 14:25:39','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=498',2,'post','',0),
	(499,1,'2015-04-13 14:52:54','2015-04-13 14:52:54','<a href=\"http://www.believemedia.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Believe Media\'s</a> <a href=\"http://www.believemedia.com/bruno-aveillan/\" target=\"_blank\">Bruno Aveillan</a> let\'s his artistic ability shine in this dazzling eye candy for L\'Oreal Color Riche with creatives from McCann. Bruno\'s eloquently visioned dreamscape illuminates the luxuriousness and boldness that embodies the L\'Oreal brand, leaving you shocked and starry-eyed from his potent us of color and imagination.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[vimeo 123080817 nolink]</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','A Pop of Color','','publish','open','open','','a-pop-of-color','','','2015-04-13 14:52:54','2015-04-13 14:52:54','',0,'http://thefamily.dev/?p=499',1,'post','',0);
